flowchart TD
    A[useError Hook Catches Error] --> B[ErrorContext Provider Updated]
    B --> C[ErrorModal Subscribes]
    C --> D{Severity}
    D -- Critical --> E[Block UI + Modal]
    D -- Warning --> F[Toast]
    D -- Info --> G[Inline Banner]
    E --> H[User Acknowledges]
    F --> H
    H --> I[Dispatch Clear Action]
    I --> J[Modal Unmounts]
